data.description: Adorable home with the country feel in the heart of Athens, TX. Close to Athens Scuba Park, schools, shopping and restaurants. This home offers easy maintenance of the yard with scenic trees across the road and behind the fence. Three bedrooms, two bathrooms, open floor concept and a spacious living room. The primary bedroom offers a spacious setting for your furniture. The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, granite tops, and plenty of room to prep the food to cook. Fenced in yard for the fur babies. Storage building.
